#-------PUNTO 1-------
### Ruta raiz con Auth:
GET http://localhost:3000/
x-auth: Pass123

### Ruta raiz sin Auth:
GET http://localhost:3000/

### Ruta Home:
GET http://localhost:3000/home.html
x-auth: Pass123

### Ruta Tasks:
GET http://localhost:3000/tasks.html
x-auth: Pass123

#-------PUNTO 2-------
### Usuarios vacio:
GET http://localhost:3000/users?page=1&limit=3
x-auth: admin_auth

#-------PUNTO 3-------
### Crear Usuario 1 (ID: 1):
POST http://localhost:3000/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Usuario Uno",
    "email": "uno@prueba.com",
    "password": "Password1",
    "confirm_password": "Password1"
}

### Crear Usuario 2 (ID: 2):
POST http://localhost:3000/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Usuario Dos",
